data.oai_dc:dc: A compressed file consisting of 10 cd hit files (2 for each of the 5 anchialine shrimp species) files used to generate orthologous clusters from the five anchialine shrimp species. One file (ending in .cd-hit_filtered) contains the putative ORFs used to generate clusters while the other file (ending in .cd-hit_filtered.clstr) contains statistics and information on the clusters.
